                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Statistical uncertainties in the",
                "extraction of the yields, and include the",
                "contribution from subtraction of contaminant yield",
                "arising from 19F(alpha,n3g)22Na."
              ]
            },
